{
  "title": "面试模拟问答",
  "goal": "根据岗位生成面试问题清单和参考回答框架。",
  "tags": [
    "求职",
    "面试",
    "训练"
  ],
  "workflow": {
    "title": "智能面试问题生成器",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "auto_input",
        "type": "input",
        "data": {
          "label": "用户输入"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "input_job_info",
        "type": "Input",
        "data": {
          "label": "岗位信息输入",
          "greeting": "请输入您需要面试的岗位名称和具体要求，我将为您生成面试问题清单和参考回答框架。",
          "enableTextInput": true,
          "textRequired": true,
          "enableFileInput": false,
          "enableStructuredForm": false
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "llm_question_generator",
        "type": "LLM",
        "data": {
          "label": "面试问题生成器",
          "model": "qwen-flash",
          "systemPrompt": "你是一位资深人力资源专家，擅长为不同岗位设计结构化面试问题。请根据用户提供的岗位信息，生成一份全面的面试问题清单，并为每个问题提供一个参考回答框架（即回答的思路和要点，而非标准答案）。\n\n输出格式必须是严格的JSON对象，包含以下两个字段：\n1. \"questions\": 一个数组，每个元素是一个对象，包含 \"category\"（问题类别，如：专业技能、行为面试、情景模拟等）、\"question\"（具体问题文本）和 \"answer_framework\"（参考回答框架）。\n2. \"summary\": 一段总结性文字，说明这份问题清单的设计思路和考察重点。",
          "temperature": 0.7,
          "responseFormat": "json_object",
          "inputMappings": {
            "user_input": "{{岗位信息输入.user_input}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "output_interview_guide",
        "type": "Output",
        "data": {
          "label": "面试指南输出",
          "inputMappings": {
            "mode": "template",
            "template": "根据您提供的岗位信息，我已为您生成以下面试问题清单和参考回答框架：\n\n## 面试问题清单\n{{面试问题生成器.response.summary}}\n\n以下是详细问题：\n{{#each 面试问题生成器.response.questions}}\n### {{this.category}}\n**问题：** {{this.question}}\n**回答框架：** {{this.answer_framework}}\n\n{{/each}}\n\n---\n*提示：以上回答框架仅供参考，旨在帮助面试官评估候选人的思维方式和能力匹配度，请根据实际情况灵活调整。*"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "auto_output",
        "type": "output",
        "data": {
          "label": "最终输出",
          "inputMappings": {
            "mode": "select",
            "sources": [
              {
                "type": "variable",
                "value": "{{用户输入.user_input}}"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "llm_1",
        "type": "llm",
        "data": {
          "label": "任务处理",
          "model": "deepseek-v3-2-251201",
          "systemPrompt": "你是一个专业助手。目标：根据岗位生成面试问题清单和参考回答框架。。请根据用户输入生成结果。",
          "temperature": 0.4,
          "inputMappings": {
            "user_input": "{{auto_input.user_input}}"
          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "source": "input_job_info",
        "target": "llm_question_generator",
        "sourceHandle": null,
        "id": "edge_input_job_info_llm_question_generator_0"
      },
      {
        "source": "llm_question_generator",
        "target": "output_interview_guide",
        "sourceHandle": null,
        "id": "edge_llm_question_generator_output_interview_guide_1"
      },
      {
        "source": "auto_input",
        "target": "input_job_info",
        "id": "edge_auto_input_input_job_info_2"
      },
      {
        "source": "output_interview_guide",
        "target": "auto_output",
        "id": "edge_output_interview_guide_auto_output_3"
      },
      {
        "id": "edge_auto_input_llm_1",
        "source": "auto_input",
        "target": "llm_1"
      },
      {
        "id": "edge_llm_1_auto_output",
        "source": "llm_1",
        "target": "auto_output"
      }
    ]
  }
}